@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
[*] --> Archived
Archived --> Active : approve
Archived : entry / log manifest
Active --> Processing : submit
Processing --> Draft : cancel
Draft --> Delivered : process
Delivered --> [*]
@enduml